i've never had problems exchanging mail with people with dotted names.
if you're trying to rewrite a specific address in /mail/lib/rewrite and need
to match a literal . with the regular expression, just escape it with \
	okamoto\.0@earth\.cias\.osakafu-u\.ac\.jp

